        PRINTORDER - the print order field name for local sqlite
        ITEMNUMBER - the itemnumber field name for local sqlite

      • compareTo

        public int compareTo(big_table_data other)

        Compare function to sort big_table_data, sorts by komanum and than by diranum

        Parameters:
        other - the big_table_data to compare to
        Returns:
        1 if I am "bigger" than other, -1 if I am smaller than other, 0 if I am exactly like the other (in koma\dira) or if those couldn't be parsed
